{"tid":2057083,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓學生遊主題樂園確診新冠肺炎　150名師生需檢測樂園急關閉","createTime":"2020-06-09T06:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T13:55:55.000Z","uid":29423,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cd59fc024d9a322b8a70e810560249255210c02","tid":2057083,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:40:53.000Z","msg":"【南韓疫情】高中生遊樂天世界9小時確診新冠肺炎　150名師生需檢測樂園急關閉<br />\n<br />\n綜合韓國媒體報道，6月5日中午12時至晚上9時，首爾中浪區一名高中生與3名朋友於樂天世界遊玩。周日（7日）早上，該名高中生確診感染新冠肺炎。首爾市教育和檢疫部門馬上關閉該名學生所屬的學校，並要求約150名同級學生、老師、密切接觸者立即接受病毒檢測。同時，當局將會為近600名學生、教職員進行檢測。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2664140/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2664140%2F&d=oKnYn5PLwsF01pzJS7XelpS3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=4dc320ae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2664140/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">海洋公園開返啦！我好興奮呀！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628548d5cc6025775623a39ee548e1ccb10b133e","tid":2057083,"uid":29423,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"明明去主題樂園唔計群組聚集<br />\n吖～又會咁唔好彩嘅？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813e76a4f25eb56e99c4326685fffcd30fe62248","tid":2057083,"uid":29423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:48:40.000Z","msg":"好多朋友已經plan緊用生日優惠 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n矛事的"},{"pid":"ca172f009fb84de2c4b5dcdc82104060fc51b632","tid":2057083,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T06:50:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/Untitled-1-05_i3nQ7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fme